claim.claim-text:
1. A personal aid, comprising: 
a handheld housing sized to be readily carried by a user; 
eyeglasses coupled to the housing for selective retrieval by a user of the personal aid; 
a smart card holder formed with the housing; and 
an electronic assistant integrated with the housing, the electronic assistant being linked to the smart card holder in which a smart card is positioned to provide functionality to the electronic assistant.
